rful. It could eat Omastar and Omanyte whole and not be bothered in the slightest by their shells."}, {"version": "white", "text": "Incredible jaw strength enables them to chew up steel beams and rocks along with their prey."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "It could knock out a foe with a slap from one of its developed front appendages and chew it up, shell or bones and all."}, {"version": "x", "text": "They can live both in the ocean and on land. A slap from one of them is enough to open a hole in the bottom of a tanker."}, {"version": "y", "text": "It could knock out a foe with a slap from one of its developed front appendages and chew it up, shell or bones and all."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "tirtouga"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "carracosta"}]}